# Cursor AI Rules for Drunken-Agy
# This file is automatically read by Cursor to enforce project boundaries.

# JIRA Task Management
- Do not make assumptions about the next feature.
- If asked "what should we do next", advise the user to run `python scripts/jira_bridge.py get-todo` in the terminal to fetch the Jira backlog.

# Documentation & Confluence
- This project uses a Docs-as-Code approach synced to Confluence.
- If the user asks to update documentation, modify the local `.md` files.
- Remind the user to run `python scripts/confluence_bridge.py push ...` in the terminal after the changes are finalized.

# Git Protocol
- Remind the user to create feature branches.
- Never write scripts that force push to the `main` branch.
